2. {\b Download Content:} Fetch email content from IPFS using stored hash\par
3. {\b Re-compute Hash:} Generate SHA-256 hash of retrieved content\par
4. {\b Compare Hashes:} Verify computed hash matches blockchain record\par
5. {\b Verify Signatures:} Validate all cryptographic signatures\par
6. {\b Check Timestamps:} Verify temporal consistency\par\par

